      "text": "uq_short_code           →  short_code UNIQUE across ALL rows\n(incl. deleted)\nchk_original_url_length →  length(original_url) <= 2048\nchk_short_code_format   →  short_code ~ '^[0-9a-zA-Z_-]{4,32}$'\nchk_deleted_consistency →  deleted_at IS SET iff is_deleted =\nTRUE",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
