      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "uq_short_code           →  short_code UNIQUE across ALL rows (incl. deleted)\nchk_original_url_length →  length(original_url) <= 2048\nchk_short_code_format   →  short_code ~ '^[0-9a-zA-Z_-]{4,32}$'\nchk_deleted_consistency →  deleted_at IS SET iff is_deleted = TRUE",
